snippet.title: Renown - Customization
snippet.description:
(Reuploaded due to Framerate error)
Quick video showcasing some of the emblem and customization work we have been working on. 
This includes the ability to change your patterns, emblems and colours. 
As well as adding a few more helmets for people to choose from.
Join our discord - https://discord.gg/Tr2DxFh
